              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " I-127(n,gamma) cross section = 0.82 barns",
                "From R.L.Macklin et al.,Phys.Rev.107,Page 504(1957)(see",
                "entries 30086 and 30087) was assumed for the measured",
                "capture data used in the spin cut-off factor derivation"
              ]
            }
          ],
